Cell["\<\
Calculates the average of the von Neumann entropy of the pure states in the \
above statistical ensemble.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1391018130,ExpressionUUID->"1181724b-eaaf-4d39-a62d-d04283d09594"],

